00:12:30.970 --> 00:12:31.520
Capitán...

00:12:33.030 --> 00:12:34.580
¿Que le pasa a ella?

00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:36.440
Ranka.

00:12:37.010 --> 00:12:39.160
